sub_title: Graduated in Geology & Geochemistry and Young IT Consultant at Net4s
summary:
My name is Lars Ruhe, I am 24 years old and I work as Young IT Consultant at Net4s. I finished my master in Geology and Geochemistry at the VU in Amsterdam in Januari 2021. Before my master, I did a bachelor in Earth sciences at the VU for which I obtained my diploma in 2018. I like working with satellite data, subsurface data and code. 

I would describe myself as someone who likes to observe, analyze a situation and then work systematically. I enjoy working with a group of people on a project, but I can also easily work independently. I come across as calm and also manage to keep a cool head under time pressure. In addition, I am always very motivated to finish my projects, which also encourages other group members. My interests are broad, including topics outside of geology. In geology and geochemistry I am very interested in geochemistry, satellite data and the subsurface. I love to puzzle with my data to find a suitable solution to the problem I am working on.
